Inputs\:
	host\:           host name to check
	username\:       user name to login into host as
	password\:       password to use for login
	PID\:            the PID of the process to kill

	Failed\:         Any other error condition

	The kill return code is placed into the operation result
	Nothing is placed into the context

Inputs\:
	host\:            host name to check
	username\:        user name to login into host as
	password\:        password to use for login
	PID\:             the PID to check

Responses\:
	Running\:         If the process is running
	Not Running\:     If the process is not running
	Host Not Found\:  If the host cannot be found
	Authentication Failure\: If the login fails
	Failed\:          Any other error condition

Results and Context\:
	The ps return code is placed into the operation result
